languages.text: «¿Cómo puedo enfadarme con usted? Su forma de sembrar la muerte es hermosa, determinada a completar su cacería hasta el final».
languages.original_text: "How can I be angry at you? You were beautiful in the way you sowed death, determined to see your hunt through to the end."

traits.locale_text: «¿Cómo puedo enfadarme con usted? Su forma de sembrar la muerte es hermosa, determinada a completar su cacería hasta el final».

languages.text: 「どうして怒ることができようか？最後まで狩りをやり遂げようと決意し、死を蒔いたお前の姿は美しかった」
languages.original_text: "How can I be angry at you? You were beautiful in the way you sowed death, determined to see your hunt through to the end."

traits.locale_text: 「どうして怒ることができようか？最後まで狩りをやり遂げようと決意し、死を蒔いたお前の姿は美しかった」

languages.text: “我怎么可能会生你的气呢？你播撒死亡，决心将狩猎进行到底，那样的你实在是太美了。”
languages.original_text: "How can I be angry at you? You were beautiful in the way you sowed death, determined to see your hunt through to the end."

traits.locale_text: “我怎么可能会生你的气呢？你播撒死亡，决心将狩猎进行到底，那样的你实在是太美了。”

languages.text: "Wie könnte ich wütend auf Euch sein? Es war bezaubernd, wie Ihr den Tod gesät habt und entschlossen wart, Eure Jagd zu Ende zu bringen."
languages.original_text: "How can I be angry at you? You were beautiful in the way you sowed death, determined to see your hunt through to the end."

languages.text: « Comment pourrais-je être en colère contre vous ? Vous étiez si belle dans votre manière de semer la mort, si déterminée à aller jusqu'au bout de votre chasse. »
languages.original_text: "How can I be angry at you? You were beautiful in the way you sowed death, determined to see your hunt through to the end."
